About Us



Solutions, Service & Guidance
Based in Morristown, New Jersey, Beacon Trust is a full service wealth management firm with approximately $2.5 billion in assets under administration and decades of proven success, superior solutions and exceptional client service. We focus on helping you attain, preserve and expand your assets through customized wealth management planning—based on your financial risk preference, not ours.

Gaining insight into your lifestyle goals, business affairs and legacy intentions requires an approach to proactive communication that involves more than just phone calls and emails. Driven by your goals, our portfolio managers and wealth advisors strive to make every interaction productive, personal and meaningful.

Beacon Trust provides a comprehensive suite of financial services designed for flexibility, including Investment Management, Sophisticated Financial Planning, Tax Advisory and Preparation, Trust and Estate Fiduciary, and Private Banking.







